data.title: Peninsula School District
data.text:
Welcome to the Peninsula School District

Welcome to the Peninsula School District, where over 8,000 students across 17 schools embark on a journey of learning and growth every day. Nestled across the stunning Puget Sound from the vibrant Seattle/Tacoma area, our district spans 120 square miles of beautiful landscapes on both the Gig Harbor and Key Peninsulas.

At Peninsula School District, we are proud to be recognized as one of the most innovative and robust districts in Washington State. Our vision is simple yet powerful: to inspire and empower every child, every day. Our mission is to ensure that every student becomes a successful and engaged global citizen through cutting-edge programs and a nurturing culture that fosters a true sense of belonging.

We are dedicated to supporting each child on their unique path to excellence, providing the tools and encouragement they need to thrive. Join us and be a part of a community where every studentâ€™s potential is recognized and cultivated daily.
